{"tid":2511908,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"學佛兩年幾，有無咩想問？","createTime":"2021-05-01T09:20:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T09:48:22.000Z","uid":17232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1f1422a25fb2b6e75c176456430ceb4c59cfd8","tid":2511908,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:20:50.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\"><em><span class=\"red\">《法句譬喻經》：「比丘！汝等所論不究苦義，天下之苦莫過有身！飢渴寒熱、瞋恚驚怖、色欲怨禍皆由於身。」</span></em></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">你們都不知苦的根本真義，天下諸苦，皆由於有色身，有了假身，就有飢渴、寒熱、瞋恚、驚怖、色欲、怨禍等外苦，所以假身是眾苦的根本，禍患的元凶。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n見身邊竟然有好多人都有興趣學佛，但係可能初學唔知點入手所以無再深入落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n開呢個po係想多啲人可以潛心修行，又或者你純粹對佛教有疑問都可以喺呢到問下我<br />\n<br />\n利申純粹交流分享下 唔識就話唔識希望唔好講錯野<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edfa057b59f01d530552d517b0ed91565be9ddee","tid":2511908,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:23:11.000Z","msg":"估唔到呢個系列竟然開到依家已經唔知第7定第8個post<br />\n個topic由學佛年幾變做學佛兩年幾<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位ching過左一年仲有冇懈怠定係越修越精進？"},{"pid":"8610ceeef8beebf3f6e70bd5b54d4ffc828aa014","tid":2511908,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:23:49.000Z","msg":"btw 每個post都要po一次嘅佛教電影 《達摩祖師傳》<br />\n每過一段時間睇所感悟到嘅野又會唔同<br />\n導演拍完呢套戲之後就喺香港出左家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CAMVrjKgmTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCAMVrjKgmTM&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRJAcLRrMd6FPy3rP8eGE4os%3D&h=e981905e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CAMVrjKgmTM</a>"},{"pid":"d0273ca3ca589bb783a6a8c2b50f91a82d1505c2","tid":2511908,"uid":252784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"點解要開個po喺上班台"},{"pid":"28d3354d143fb9cee34ab3326eb913c40718e803","tid":2511908,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0273ca3ca589bb783a6a8c2b50f91a82d1505c2","tid":2511908,"uid"